{"tid":1255903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對準目標，要求獨立調查612","createTime":"2019-06-24T17:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T17:37:57.000Z","uid":12023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"825b5e6899c621baf499635f3e00c0296e14d622","tid":1255903,"uid":12023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"一切不合作運動，都需要有訴求焦點，先可以聚集力量，小弟蠢見，覺得要集中要求成立獨立委員會，動用特權法調查612事件！<br />\n<br />\n睇翻之前4大要求:<br />\n1. 撤回條例 <br />\n林鄭已指出到下年7月，條例草案就會失效<br />\n加上諒佢都唔夠膽喺任內再推<br />\n<br />\n2.林鄭下台<br />\n佢自己都想下台啦，但北京肯先得嫁<br />\n其實阿&rdquo;好打得&rdquo;已經眾叛親離，唔落台都有樣好，至少可以繼續we connect，加強泛民力量<br />\n<br />\n3. 收回612暴動定性，釋放被捕學生<br />\n4. 追究警察濫用暴力<br />\n呢兩點正正就係要透過獨立調查來推動，唔可以比監警會自己人查自己人。今次難得保皇黨都唔撐林鄭，係時候對準焦點，要求徹查612，追究責任。咁樣先可以做到3同4！"},{"pid":"4aa9d98747359ce9f79ee02591ecbfa670ea30c9","tid":1255903,"uid":12023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe593e5e5fe7d15831cc284b58a6f76a4bb22673","tid":1255903,"uid":12023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"bf40bf22b87229ba290bd74d37f5d8fe4a677f7a","tid":1255903,"uid":12023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:34:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5137de419a8698fd3223018f74cff532170d5697","tid":1255903,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"現階段三四係最重要"}]}